    <scopecontent id="aspace_46df2e2056eb460e546224de4cb13fa1">
      <head>Collection Overview</head>
      <p>The Claudia Koonz papers include some records related to the Refugee Action Project and a
        proposed center for research on human security. The collection includes correspondence,
        reports, emails, and other materials.</p>
